# Loading packages
```{r, eval=TRUE, message=FALSE}
packages = c('sp','rgdal', 'rgeos','sf', 'spdep', 'tmap', 'tidyverse','rvest','spatstat', 'raster', 'maptools','blogdown')
for (p in packages){
  if(!require(p, character.only = T)){
    install.packages(p)
  }
  library(p,character.only = T)
}
```
